title: Kissing the Pink - Live in London
description:
Kissing the Pink's ultra rare live album. A must have for the fans of this 80s new wave/new romantic band. 

Kissing the Pink was: Nick Whitecross (vocals, guitars), Jon Kingsley Hall (keyboards, vocals), Peter Barnett (bass, violin, vocals), Simon Aldridge (guitars, vocals), Stephen Cusack (drums, vocals), George Stewart (keyboards, vocals), Josephine Wells (saxophone, vocals), Sylvia Griffin (vocals)
